Company Overview of NEXT Group Holdings, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
NEXT Group Holdings, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides telecommunications and telecommunications mobility, and remittance solutions. The company is based in Miami, Florida.


1111 Brickell AvenueSuite 2200Miami, FL 33131United States



Phone: 800-611-3622

Fax: 305-647-6497

www.nextgroupholdings.com







