	Director Independence



	 


	We currently do not have any independent directors, as the term
	“independent” is defined in Section 803A of the NYSE Amex LLC Company Guide. Since the OTC Markets does not have rules
	regarding director independence, the Board makes its determination as to director independence based on the definition of “independence”
	as defined under the rules of the New York Stock Exchange (“NYSE”) and American Stock Exchange (“Amex”).



	 










